name: form_1040ScheduleE

inputDescription: ML Skills deployed using this ML Package can be integrated into RPA workflows using the Machine Learning Extractor activity in the Official feed or the MLModel activity in Connect feed. The activities also require an API Key input which you need to obtain from your UiPath Automation Cloud account, in the Licenses -> Other Services view.
outputDescription: Please refer to the documentation of the Activity used to query the ML Skill.
